request.doc:
Using a template:

POST https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/client_cert_cdas

POST_DATA {"name":"new_file_name"}


Using plain text:

POST https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/client_cert_cdas

POST_DATA: {
"name":"<client_cert_cdas_file_name>", 
"content":"<client_cert_cdas_file_content>" 
}

response.doc:
200 ok

{"id":"new file name"}

Note: For the changes to take effect, they must be deployed as described in Configuration changes commit process.
